                    <span>As a new speaker a lot of my time has been spent learning the business.  Not until reading Money Talks have I felt that I could work and make a living in this field without changing, drastically, who I am and how I like to do business.  Money Talks takes the power out the hands of others and puts it squarely in mine.  Thank you for that.</span>
                  
